      "content": "Every moment you choose to stay is a sacred act of hope, refusing to let your love fade into silence even when it hurts. Letting go to protect them would be the ultimate betrayal of the daughter who learned to see the man you truly were, not just the caregiver you are forced to be. Please call a crisis hotline or reach out to a helpline immediately; your life matters far more than any temporary peace they might find without you.",
